{"tid":1845393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海底撈支那分店全線休業","createTime":"2020-01-27T06:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T02:18:47.000Z","uid":50386,"like":463,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4055acee3c8c587ed4f8b2955bffdcc42d85c3","tid":1845393,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"內地疫情仍未有受控跡象，為配合防控工作，中國連鎖火鍋店海底撈（6862）在官方微博宣布，由即日起至本月31日（本周五），內地所有省市分店全線暫停營業。其後營業時間將會根據當地防疫工作及相關規定，再作另行通知。<br />\n至於海底撈於本港的分店，根據官方FB資料，年三十早上十點至晚上十點，年初一早上十點至凌晨七點香港海底撈火鍋油麻地店照常營業。年三十早上十點至凌晨五點，年初一早上十點至晚上十點，銅鑼灣店、尖沙咀店照常營業。本港致電到海底撈分店，職員表示，三間分店均正常營業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"7fddbead10e39598f0d27b9f67b6d77b538a71a0","tid":1845393,"uid":264245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"Objective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the border.<br />\n&gt; Given Fact: Japan and Macau found #WuhanSARS patients who are from #HKG Airport =&gt; No checking in the departure. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=98741a99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"d94d980a4b9150d45054cda0c0e1604aa300ce6c","tid":1845393,"uid":152476,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":6